    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Any materials manufactured through advanced technology, that differ physically from materials known throughout human history, specifically before the 20th century. This term is most often used to describe various polymers and synthetic materials.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
